job.title: RITES Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for  Engineer & Assistant Vacancies in Gurgaon
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Deputy General Manager & Assistant

Description

New Gurgaon Government Jobs have been published by Rail India Technical and Economic Service for the vacancies of Deputy General Manager & Assistant. If you are finding a government job in Gurgaon then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Gurgaon, from 14.05.2021, and till 31.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Gurgaon and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for RITES Deputy General Manager & Assistant vacancies in Gurgaon:

  • To apply for a Deputy General Manager & Assistant. posts in Gurgaon, your 10th, 12th, Degree, B.E/B.Tech must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is the 14.05.2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 31.05.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • The minimum age should be 27 years.
  • The maximum age should be 40 years.

RITES Deputy General Manager & Assistant Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Gurgaon Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 35,000 per month

How to apply for RITES Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these vacancies in Gurgaon. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of RITES
  • and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by RITES.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
